descs:
Barboach's body is covered with a slimy film. If a foe grabs it,
this Pokémon just slips out of the enemy's grip. This Pokémon
grows weak if the slimy coating dries up.

Barboach's sensitive whiskers serve as a superb radar system.
This Pokémon hides in mud, leaving only its two whiskers
exposed while it waits for prey to come along.
